ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAddition to Little Saskatchewan Indian Reserve No. 48, Manitoba
PrecisOrder setting apart 1,490.41 hectares (3,682.87 acres) for the use and benefit of the Little Saskatchewan First Nation as an addition to LITTLE SASKATCHEWAN INDIAN RESERVE NO. 48, located in the Rural Municipality of Grahamdale at approximately 10 kilometres from the Town of Gypsumville, Manitoba.
